{"id":163,"parent_id":158,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":163,"title":"2 Corinthians 5","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Cor.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 5"],[".studySummary",["i","Saints walk by faith and seek tabernacles of immortal glory—The gospel reconciles man to God—God’s ministers carry the word of reconciliation to the world."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.1","order":"03.10.005.18691"},["b","1"],"For we know that if our earthly house of",["i","this"],"tabernacle were dissolved, we have a building of God, an house not made with hands, eternal in the heavens."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.2","order":"03.10.005.18692"},["b","2"],"For in this we groan, earnestly desiring to be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"clothed"],"upon with our house which is from heaven:"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.3","order":"03.10.005.18693"},["b","3"],"If so be that being clothed we shall not be found naked."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.4","order":"03.10.005.18694"},["b","4"],"For we that are in",["i","this"],"tabernacle do",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"groan"],", being burdened: not for that we would be unclothed, but clothed upon, that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"mortality"],"might be swallowed up of life."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.5","order":"03.10.005.18695"},["b","5"],"Now he that hath wrought us for the selfsame thing",["i","is"],"God, who also hath given unto us the earnest of the Spirit."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.6","order":"03.10.005.18696"},["b","6"],"Therefore",["i","we are"],"always",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"confident"],", knowing that, whilst we are at home in the body, we are absent from the Lord:"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.7","order":"03.10.005.18697"},["b","7"],"(For we walk by",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"faith"],", not by",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"sight"],":)"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.8","order":"03.10.005.18698"},["b","8"],"We are confident,",["i","I say,"],"and willing rather to be absent from the body, and to be present with the Lord."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.9","order":"03.10.005.18699"},["b","9"],"Wherefore we",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"labour"],", that, whether present or absent, we may be accepted of him."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.10","order":"03.10.005.18700"},["b","10"],"For we must all appear before the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"judgment"],"seat of Christ; that every one may receive the things",["i","done"],"in",["i","his"],"body,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"according"],"to that he hath",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"done"],", whether",["i","it be"],"good or bad."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.11","order":"03.10.005.18701"},["b","11"],"Knowing therefore the terror of the Lord, we persuade men; but we are made manifest unto God; and I trust also are made manifest in your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"consciences"],"."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.12","order":"03.10.005.18702"},["b","12"],"For we commend not ourselves again unto you, but give you occasion to glory on our behalf, that ye may have somewhat to",["i","answer"],"them which glory in appearance, and not in heart."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.13","order":"03.10.005.18703"},["b","13"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"For"],"whether we be beside ourselves,",["i","it is"],"to God: or whether we be sober,",["i","it is"],"for your cause."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.14","order":"03.10.005.18704"},["b","14"],"For the love of Christ constraineth us; because we thus judge, that if",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"one"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"died"],"for all, then were all dead:"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.15","order":"03.10.005.18705"},["b","15"],"And",["i","that"],"he died for all, that they which live should not henceforth",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"live"],"unto themselves, but unto him which died for them, and rose again."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.16","order":"03.10.005.18706"},["b","16"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"Wherefore"],"henceforth know we no man after the flesh: yea, though we have known Christ after the flesh, yet now henceforth know we",["i","him"],"no more."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.17","order":"03.10.005.18707"},["b","17"],"Therefore if any man",["i","be"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"in Christ"],",",["i","he is"],"a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"new"],"creature:",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"old"],"things are",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_17d"},"passed"],"away; behold, all things are become",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_17e"},"new"],"."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.18","order":"03.10.005.18708"},["b","18"],"And all things",["i","are"],"of God, who hath",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"reconciled"],"us to himself by Jesus Christ, and hath given to us the ministry of reconciliation;"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.19","order":"03.10.005.18709"},["b","19"],"To wit, that God was in Christ,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"reconciling"],"the world unto himself, not imputing their trespasses unto them; and hath committed unto us the word of reconciliation."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.20","order":"03.10.005.18710"},["b","20"],"Now then we are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"ambassadors"],"for Christ, as though God did beseech",["i","you"],"by us: we pray",["i","you"],"in Christ’s stead, be ye reconciled to God."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.21","order":"03.10.005.18711"},["b","21"],"For he hath made him",["i","to be"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"sin"],"for us, who knew no",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"sin"],"; that we might be made the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_21c"},"righteousness"],"of God in him."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.2a","order":"03.10.005.18712"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/8.23"},"Rom. 8:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.4a","order":"03.10.005.18714"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mourning"},"TG Mourning"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.4b","order":"03.10.005.18716"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mortality"},"TG Mortality"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.6a","order":"03.10.005.18718"},["b","6a"],["span.small","GR"],"of good courage, of good cheer."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.7a","order":"03.10.005.18720"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/faith"},"TG Faith"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.7b","order":"03.10.005.18722"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sight"},"TG Sight"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.9a","order":"03.10.005.18724"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/9.6"},"Moro. 9:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.10a","order":"03.10.005.18726"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-judge"},"TG Jesus Christ, Judge"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.10b","order":"03.10.005.18728"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/accountability"},"TG Accountability"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.10c","order":"03.10.005.18730"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/good-works"},"TG Good Works"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.11a","order":"03.10.005.18732"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/conscience"},"TG Conscience"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.13a","order":"03.10.005.18734"},["b","13a"],["span.small","JST"],"2 Cor. 5:13 For",["i","we bear record that we are not"],"beside ourselves;",["i","for whether we glory,"],"it is to God, or whether we be sober, it is for your",["i","sakes."]],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.14a","order":"03.10.005.18736"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.15"},"Rom. 5:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.14b","order":"03.10.005.18738"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/19.16"},"D&C 19:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.15a","order":"03.10.005.18740"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/14.7.7-9"},"Rom. 14:7 (7–9)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.16a","order":"03.10.005.18742"},["b","16a"],["span.small","JST"],"2 Cor. 5:16 Wherefore, henceforth",["i","live"],"we no",["i","more"],"after the flesh;",["i","yea, though we once lived after the flesh, yet since"],"we have known Christ, now henceforth",["i","live"],"we no more",["i","after the flesh."]],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.17a","order":"03.10.005.18744"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-jn/2.5.2-5"},"1 Jn. 2:5 (2–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.17b","order":"03.10.005.18746"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/man-new-spiritually-reborn"},"TG Man, New, Spiritually Reborn"],"."],["div",{"id":"17c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.17c","order":"03.10.005.18748"},["b","17c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.6"},"Rom. 7:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/13.12.12-14"},"13:12 (12–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.13"},"Heb. 8:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"17d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.17d","order":"03.10.005.18750"},["b","17d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/29.24"},"D&C 29:24"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/63.49"},"63:49"],"."],["div",{"id":"17e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.17e","order":"03.10.005.18752"},["b","17e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/21.5"},"Rev. 21:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.18a","order":"03.10.005.18754"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reconciliation"},"TG Reconciliation"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.19a","order":"03.10.005.18756"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reconciliation"},"TG Reconciliation"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.20a","order":"03.10.005.18758"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/14.23"},"Luke 14:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.21a","order":"03.10.005.18760"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/53.6"},"Isa. 53:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.21b","order":"03.10.005.18762"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-jn/3.3"},"1 Jn. 3:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"21c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.21c","order":"03.10.005.18764"},["b","21c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/1.17"},"Rom. 1:17"],"."]]}
